cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about generating responses in a targeted style, which is a task related to natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper proposes a method that involves sharing a structured latent space, which is a technique commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves generating responses based on context, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
